title: Lennard Digital Sylenth1 v2.2.1 32bit Windows 8
description:
I'd been going crazy not being able to use Sylenth1 on Windows 8 and I finally found a working version.

Tested and works! No more of those Please Register sounds.
Included some presets from the Team Peace Out release and thanks the the guys on Audioz for all the information.

1. Install to your VST folder
2. Copy the soundbank folder to the install folder
3. Load your Daw then open the Sylenth plugin.
4. Click register and import the .dat file.
5. Close the plugin and then open it again, you're registered and good to go! Please seed.
